  <name>Text to Speech</name>
  <summary>Convert text to speech using Microsoft Edge TTS</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Text to Speech is a desktop application for converting text into high-quality audio using Microsoft Edge TTS. It provides an easy-to-use interface for generating speech from text with customizable voices, pitch, rate, and volume.
      The application is designed for content creators, educators, and anyone needing to produce audio from text.
    </p>
    <p>
      Key features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Microsoft Edge TTS integration for natural-sounding voices</li>
      <li>Character library with predefined voice variations</li>
      <li>Batch processing for multiple text inputs</li>
      <li>User-friendly graphical interface</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      The tool supports various output formats and can be used entirely offline once installed.
    </p>
  </description>

